name: Darth Giger 2.0 Molly Hologlitch Fury Double Stack (Roll'n Hard Mix)
description: Remixing Darth Giger with all levels on 11! I wanted to recreate my first double stacked experience where I stuck my head in a speaker at a rave.  Closest visual I've created to taking a double stacked blue dolphin back in the day. Those who know will recognize it. Those that don't will still get something from it.
